{"tid":464910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(窮撚家庭入)寧願留係窮撚屋企定比有錢人收養","createTime":"2017-11-11T04:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T04:02:04.000Z","uid":6777,"like":79,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8e3e0e928242c3df666eb7e94b88c4cbaa877104","tid":464910,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:28:08.000Z","msg":"身為窮撚家庭出世既你，姐係連登仔成日叫窮撚咪生仔既果種貧窮程度<br />\n<br />\n如果係你有意識到窮唔窮果陣開始比你揀<br />\n<br />\n會揀繼續留係個窮撚家庭，定會揀比有錢人收養？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比有錢人收養<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留係窮撚家庭"},{"pid":"43c36496fa431c197e54af65c75639f59f614782","tid":464910,"uid":6777,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:32:53.000Z","msg":"窮撚生仔，然後最基本既都比唔到，仲要日撚日鬧你生叉燒好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 教又唔識教"},{"pid":"4de172e4794ae0dbfd7b8695e484dfc18d9e072e","tid":464910,"uid":14275,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:35:42.000Z","msg":"緊係有錢佬啦<br />\n窮撚家庭通常雙親都要返工 冇時間陪你<br />\n有錢佬又係雙親都要返工 都係冇時䦘陪你<br />\n但有錢佬比到你物質上嘅野唔知多幾多皮啦<br />\n老閪都要有錢佬"},{"pid":"8a4f74207fcca411e3ccb689138fee4574cf882c","tid":464910,"uid":6777,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:43:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>緊係有錢佬啦<br />\n窮撚家庭通常雙親都要返工 冇時間陪你<br />\n有錢佬又係雙親都要返工 都係冇時䦘陪你<br />\n但有錢佬比到你物質上嘅野唔知多幾多皮啦<br />\n老閪都要有錢佬</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係淨係得錢？<br />\n我覺得有錢同好多野都掛勾<br />\n教育，學識，遠見，計劃"},{"pid":"160dd6cfc72a1c68a403f6f80a85afeeb3953898","tid":464910,"uid":52146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:48:09.000Z","msg":"屌你咁都要諗？<br />\n弱會都揀有錢佬啦"},{"pid":"b796ff6eaf23d619c94b22159644441929cc7c0b","tid":464910,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:48:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你咁都要諗？<br />\n弱會都揀有錢佬啦</blockquote><br />\n血緣真係唔重要？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cefd9b0132ad8ebf4ed3a5646d6463ddd99b949","tid":464910,"uid":59465,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:50:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你咁都要諗？<br />\n弱會都揀有錢佬啦</blockquote><br />\n血緣真係唔重要？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n血緣都唔係自己決定嘅<br />\n到底有乜咁重要？<br />\n你逼我流你嘅血架<br />\n<br />\n對自己好嘅就係好父母<br />\n生娘不及養娘大<br />\n明唔明"},{"pid":"ab3c343d53176043d45cb0776cf700a1c0574f53","tid":464910,"uid":93855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:50:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>緊係有錢佬啦<br />\n窮撚家庭通常雙親都要返工 冇時間陪你<br />\n有錢佬又係雙親都要返工 都係冇時䦘陪你<br />\n但有錢佬比到你物質上嘅野唔知多幾多皮啦<br />\n老閪都要有錢佬</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係淨係得錢？<br />\n我覺得有錢同好多野都掛勾<br />\n教育，學識，遠見，計劃</blockquote><br />\n岩 做窮人通常識埋啲mk 少見識冇內涵既人<br />\n仲有有錢人唔會成日借你錢跟住又唔還"},{"pid":"f14ed43744e7ed217ccefb2d8156dd6e859d8147","tid":464910,"uid":45001,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:51:43.000Z","msg":"做窮人<br />\n平平凡凡不好嗎？"},{"pid":"d600b0e3db99669126f975b28d60867a0dd340a7","tid":464910,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:52:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>緊係有錢佬啦<br />\n窮撚家庭通常雙親都要返工 冇時間陪你<br />\n有錢佬又係雙親都要返工 都係冇時䦘陪你<br />\n但有錢佬比到你物質上嘅野唔知多幾多皮啦<br />\n老閪都要有錢佬</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係淨係得錢？<br />\n我覺得有錢同好多野都掛勾<br />\n教育，學識，遠見，計劃</blockquote><br />\n岩 做窮人通常識埋啲mk 少見識冇內涵既人<br />\n仲有有錢人唔會成日借你錢跟住又唔還</blockquote><br />\n人脈 社交<br />\n真係差好遠"},{"pid":"0cc58bda8b1234ce67576b6a6ff82083d00f0d9f","tid":464910,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:52:21.000Z","msg":"唔好偷偷留負皮<br />\n可摸耳講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c39afb729bd470de640134aa43537a8ce7b2bf","tid":464910,"uid":45001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:52:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好偷偷留負皮<br />\n可摸耳講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a55b092c8066e21a306d5d3537035e65c7a662","tid":464910,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:53:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做窮人<br />\n平平凡凡不好嗎？</blockquote><br />\n富人也可平凡生活<br />\n窮人就連選擇嘅機會都無<br />\n而且所謂平凡<br />\n其實只係做奴隸<br />\n日復一日付出時間心血<br />\n為嘅只係兩餐溫飽<br />\n其他成果就俾哂有錢佬"},{"pid":"f196f051f98eb5881729d36a907196f1c7eefa16","tid":464910,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:53:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做窮人<br />\n平平凡凡不好嗎？</blockquote><br />\n點為之平凡？<br />\n想參加課外活動都唔得叫平凡？<br />\n想有張正常高度既書台做功課都無叫平凡？"},{"pid":"ee572500e81867a8ab78b66d907586f61452ff6c","tid":464910,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好偷偷留負皮<br />\n可摸耳講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你一個人留到2個負皮係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪衝出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14fb3abf196274d177511e3ff7a72fa16b154dc5","tid":464910,"uid":97465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:54:52.000Z","msg":"有錢人唔會收養你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79c292adc9bc55ff7a6ea52262955a53a492263","tid":464910,"uid":45001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:55:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做窮人<br />\n平平凡凡不好嗎？</blockquote><br />\n富人也可平凡生活<br />\n窮人就連選擇嘅機會都無<br />\n而且所謂平凡<br />\n其實只係做奴隸<br />\n日復一日付出時間心血<br />\n為嘅只係兩餐溫飽<br />\n其他成果就俾哂有錢佬</blockquote><br />\n你做左咁多假設<br />\n邊個話會窮撚一定窮一世先 你知先可以預知未來"},{"pid":"c45aeef4555906e5b897f4625b86fb8d8e9a68b7","tid":464910,"uid":45001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔好偷偷留負皮<br />\n可摸耳講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你一個人留到2個負皮係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪衝出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/125615_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F125615_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=c273592d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我見唔到有第二個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac66cae23add9e4295e06a1c29937301a668d561","tid":464910,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T04:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做窮人<br />\n平平凡凡不好嗎？</blockquote><br />\n富人也可平凡生活<br />\n窮人就連選擇嘅機會都無<br />\n而且所謂平凡<br />\n其實只係做奴隸<br />\n日復一日付出時間心血<br />\n為嘅只係兩餐溫飽<br />\n其他成果就俾哂有錢佬</blockquote><br />\n你做左咁多假設<br />\n邊個話會窮撚一定窮一世先 你知先可以預知未來</blockquote><br />\n你上邊話自己要平凡嘛<br />\n咁我問返轉頭<br />\n做有錢佬個仔<br />\n可以由一開始就安安樂樂平凡過生活<br />\n點解你要揀做窮人<br />\n之後又要發奮搵錢<br />\n死捱爛捱捱出頭<br />\n之後先去過平凡生活？<br />\n我明現實係無得選擇<br />\n但依家講緊有得揀<br />\n我理解唔到點解要拿屎上身"},{"pid":"e622483bee1b79514839268df37926611dc89785","tid":464910,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:00:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔好偷偷留負皮<br />\n可摸耳講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你一個人留到2個負皮係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪衝出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/125615_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F125615_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=c273592d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我見唔到有第二個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我打果句已經兩個<br />\n而家已經3個啦<br />\n你收手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf77c7209a8725bc2b6bb6abb35ce0dddcf92c9","tid":464910,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:02:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做窮人<br />\n平平凡凡不好嗎？</blockquote><br />\n富人也可平凡生活<br />\n窮人就連選擇嘅機會都無<br />\n而且所謂平凡<br />\n其實只係做奴隸<br />\n日復一日付出時間心血<br />\n為嘅只係兩餐溫飽<br />\n其他成果就俾哂有錢佬</blockquote><br />\n你做左咁多假設<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">邊個話會窮撚一定窮一世先</span> 你知先可以預知未來</blockquote><br />\n你上邊話自己要平凡嘛<br />\n咁我問返轉頭<br />\n做有錢佬個仔<br />\n可以由一開始就安安樂樂平凡過生活<br />\n點解你要揀做窮人<br />\n之後又要發奮搵錢<br />\n死捱爛捱捱出頭<br />\n之後先去過平凡生活？<br />\n我明現實係無得選擇<br />\n但依家講緊有得揀<br />\n我理解唔到點解要拿屎上身</blockquote><br />\n我條問題已經好清楚就係為免有文盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知都係有文盲<br />\n講緊窮撚家庭，唔係講緊條友日後會唔會脫貧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65fa94e72ff6867c98b58f5260230ea88eb3ee7","tid":464910,"uid":45001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做窮人<br />\n平平凡凡不好嗎？</blockquote><br />\n富人也可平凡生活<br />\n窮人就連選擇嘅機會都無<br />\n而且所謂平凡<br />\n其